# Visual baselines are content-addressed PNGs named <sha256>.png.
# Default policy: reviewed baseline PNGs may be checked in while this directory stays below 100MB.
# If the directory would exceed 100MB, set HANDSHAKE_VISUAL_BASELINE_ROOT to an operator-controlled external baseline store.
# Keep this stub so no-context models can discover the baseline contract even when PNGs are externalized.
!.gitignore
